high_descs: Turn right and walk into the dining room to face the diningtable.
Pick up the kettle from the table.
Turn around and walk straight to take a left turn to reach the bathroom sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink and take it out.
Walk left to exit the bathroom and turn right to walk to the shelf next to the couch.
Put the kettle on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Kettle on the Shelf.

high_descs: Place the kettle on the sink, open the faucets. Close the faucets. Take the teapot.
Place the kettle on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Find a kettle, wet it and bring it to the shelf.

high_descs: Pick up the kettle from table.
Walk towards the bathroom and put the bottle in the sink.
Fill up the kettle with water.
Walk with bottle towards the room and place in shelf.
Open the shelf and place the kettle inside.
anns.task_desc: Pick up kettle and place it on the sink. Then fill it up with water and place the kettle in the shelf.
